{"**F36 Card** `v6.9.0`":["- Restore `actionsButtonProps['aria-label']` override behavior for card action buttons.- Pass `actionsButtonProps` through the `Card` header action path."],"**F36 Pill** `v6.9.0`":["- **Deprecated**\n- `Pill`: Deprecated in favor of `PillNext` from `@contentful/f36-pill-next`. Will be removed in the next major version (v7).- Migration guide available at: https://f36.contentful.com/components/pill#migration"]}